<center>xc_natureblock
by ChiChiN</center>

Sequel of my older map xc_nature. I finished the map as a tribute to xjcss and all my friends there. I'm pretty sad that this community completely went down, but as many people mentioned, it had to shutdown because of some problems, so I released this as a "cherry on the top" :)

Rate, leave comment. Thanks.
